        <p class="text-gray-700 italic">"A must-have tool for digital marketers looking to stay ahead with data-driven strategies."</p>
        <footer class="mt-6 text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-600">— James P., Marketing Specialist</footer>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section id="faq" class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 reveal">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-indigo-600 mb-10 text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-6">
      <details class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer transition-shadow hover:shadow-lg">
        <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 text-lg">How accurate is your traffic data?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">We use multiple data sources and machine learning models to ensure high accuracy in tracking and reporting traffic data.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer transition-shadow hover:shadow-lg">
        <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 text-lg">Can I export reports?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Yes, you can export detailed reports in various formats such as CSV and PDF for your convenience.</p>
      </details>

